cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper deals with document summarisation, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques, such as interpretable machine learning (cs.LG) and data subset selection (cs.DS), which are relevant subfields. Additionally, the paper formulates the problem as a binary classification task, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
